        <message/>
        <message_html><![CDATA[<h1><span style="font-family: helvetica;">${mail_script:get_updated_by_name} transferred ownership of an ATAT portfolio to you</span></h1>
<div style="border: solid black 1px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;">
<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">${mail_script:get_updated_by_name} made you the owner of ${name} within the Account Tracking and Automation Tool (ATAT). As the owner, you can now:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">Track cloud usage and manage spending throughout the duration of the JWCC task order</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">Edit all portfolio details, to include adding CSP administrators, requesting to modify task orders, and adding new task orders</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">Manage portfolio member access</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;">Archive this portfolio</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>View portfolio: <a href="services.disa.mil/dapps-atat">Link to ATAT</a></strong></span></p>
</div>]]></message_html>
